        "detailedDescription_md": "Dai Didi Clinic Scheme is an important welfare scheme of the Government of Chhattisgarh. This scheme is to provide medical help to those women and girls living in rural areas who do not go to the doctor due to lack of time or many other reasons, but now midwives provide them treatment facilities, through female friends and medical staff near home. And she can get her treatment done through female staff without humid.\n",
